Given	I'm logged-in with valid credentials
And	I'm on Page 03 of Thoracic CT
When I click on 'Settings' box
And I select 'Individual' radio button
Then 'Protocol' dropdown menu is enabled
And 'Motion artifacts' checkbox is enabled
And 'Respiratory artifacts' checkbox is enabled
And 'Pulsation artifacts' checkbox is enabled
And 'Metal artifacts' checkbox is enabled
And 'Other artifacts' checkbox is enabled

When I select any Protocol (e.g. Low-dose) from 'Protocol' dropdown menu
Then 'Add new protocol' button is enabled
And 'Parameter' tab is enabled and selected by default
And 'Reconstructions' tab is enabled

When I click on 'Reconstructions' tab if not selected
Then 'Reconstructions' dropdown menu is enabled

When I select 'Sagittal' from 'Reconstructions' dropdown menu
Then 'Add new reconstructions' button is enabled
And 'Slice thickness ST 1' input field is enabled
And 'Slice thickness ST 2' input field is enabled
And 'Slice thickness ST 3' input field is enabled
And 'Slice thickness ST 4' input field is enabled


And 'Soft tissues' checkbox is enabled
And 'Lungs' checkbox is enabled
And 'Bone' checkbox is enabled
And 'CT angiography' checkbox is enabled

And 'MIP' checkbox is enabled
And 'MPR' checkbox is enabled
And 'VRT' checkbox is enabled
And 'MinIP' checkbox is enabled

And 'Dose length product (DLP)' input field is enabled
